00:29:09.720 --> 00:29:11.220
some reporting
requirements, there's

00:29:11.220 --> 00:29:15.300
some elements to being
a B Corp, but these

00:29:15.300 --> 00:29:18.600
are things that I believe
a business just should do.

00:29:18.600 --> 00:29:22.930
And that's my value as the
leader of Greyston now,

00:29:22.930 --> 00:29:27.370
but I don't frankly
understand other leaders that

00:29:27.370 --> 00:29:29.890
don't appreciate at least
bringing elements of that

00:29:29.890 --> 00:29:31.630
