plan around that.

00:31:12.130 --> 00:31:14.290
And it just sort of
helps test our thinking

00:31:14.290 --> 00:31:16.150
and push us to do more.

00:31:16.150 --> 00:31:19.070
But it's things that are
already within the company

00:31:19.070 --> 00:31:21.670
ethos and the DNA
