00:41:22.650 --> 00:41:26.332
to support those that need help
from others that perhaps are

00:41:26.332 --> 00:41:28.290
privileged enough to have
opportunities to work

00:41:28.290 --> 00:41:31.056
at an amazing place like this
after all your hard work.

00:41:31.056 --> 00:41:31.960
HOST: Thank you.

